'''扎因·杰韦德·「贊恩」·马利克'''（{{lang-en|Zain Javadd<!-- STOP! "JAVADD" IS HIS MIDDLE NAME, DO NOT CHANGE MIDDLE NAME IT IS SOURCED WITH UK ARCHIVE -->  "Zayn" Malik}}，{{IPAc-en|'|m|æ|l|ɪ|k}}；{{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq|زین جواد ملک}}}}；{{bd|1993年|1月12日|||catIdx=M}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teennowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/507766/diva-fever-s-craig-saggers-one-direction-s-zain-zayn-malik-wears-the-dog-tag-i-gave-him|title=Diva Fever's Craig Saggers: One Direction's Zain 'Zayn' Malik wears the dog-tag I gave him|work={{tsl|en|NOW (UK magazine)||Teen Now Magazine}}|publisher={{tsl|en|IPC Media||IPC Media Limited}}|date=2010-12-19|accessdate=2011-03-17|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226125235/https://www.celebsnow.co.uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，英国歌手，曾為男子團體[[1世代|1世代]]成員，在組合期間，他發佈了4張錄音室專輯。2015年3月25日，贊恩正式宣告退團，並於2015年7月30日和[[RCA唱片|RCA唱片]]簽下合約，正式向個人歌手事業邁出一大步。2016年3月25日，馬利克發佈了個人首張專輯《{{Link-en|心解密|Mind of Mine}}》，專輯在多國奪冠。

== 早年生涯 ==
贊恩·馬利克出生于英国[[西约克郡|西约克郡]][[布拉德福德|布拉德福德]]。<ref name="Clayton">{{cite news|author=Emma Clayton|url=http://www.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/news/8431606.X_Factor_s_Zain_reigns_in_Spain|title=East Bowling teenager Zain Malik makes it to finals, but Bradford girl band Husstle bow out|work={{tsl|en|Telegraph & Argus||Bradford Telegraph & Argus}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Newsquest||Newsquest}} Media Group|date=2010-10-05|accessdate=2012-10-05|archive-date=2012-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007194545/http://www.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/news/8431606.X_Factor_s_Zain_reigns_in_Spain/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的父亲耶沙·马利克（{{lang|en|Yaser Malik}}），是一名[[巴基斯坦裔英國人|巴基斯坦裔英國人]]，母亲特里西娅·馬利克（{{lang|en|Tricia Brannan Malik}}）拥有爱尔兰和英国血统。<ref>{{cite web|last=Mabey|first=Meghan|url=http://www.popstartats.com/zayn-malik-tattoos/arabic-tats/?ModPagespeed=noscript|title=Zayn Malik’s Two Arabic Chest Tattoos|date=2012-04-24|publisher=Pop Tartas|access-date=2015-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716022052/http://www.popstartats.com/zayn-malik-tattoos/arabic-tats/?ModPagespeed=noscript|archive-date=2015-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他有一个姐姐，名为朵妮雅（{{lang|en|Doniya}}），还有两个妹妹：瓦利娅（{{lang|en|Waliyha}}）和萨法阿（{{lang|en|Safaa}}）。<ref name="Glimpse">{{cite news|author=Liz Thomas|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2121920/Beatlemania-takes-new-Direction-Thousands-gather-Montreal-catch-glimpse-band.html|title=Beatlemania takes a whole new Direction! Thousands gather in Montreal to catch a glimpse of the band|work=Daily Mail|publisher={{tsl|en|Associated Newspapers||Associated Newspapers}}|accessdate=2012-03-31|location=London|date=2012-03-29|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921075524/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2121920/Beatlemania-takes-new-Direction-Thousands-gather-Montreal-catch-glimpse-band.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/535611/zayn-malik-s-mum-when-my-boy-leaves-home-i-cry-at-the-gate/1|title=Zayn Malik's mum: When my boy leaves home, I cry at the gate|work={{tsl|en|NOW (UK magazine)||Now Magazine}}|publisher={{tsl|en|IPC Media||IPC Media Limited}}|date=2012-04-22|accessdate=2012-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427022054/http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/535611/zayn-malik-s-mum-when-my-boy-leaves-home-i-cry-at-the-gate/1|archive-date=2012-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

馬利克从小生活在{{Link-en|东保龄|East Bowling}}，<ref name=Clayton/> 先后在下菲尔茨小学（{{lang|en|Lower Fields Primary School}}）和{{Link-en|唐高中|Tong High School}}就读。<ref name="Tong">{{cite news|author=Ben Barnett|url=http://www.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/news/8689788.Tong_School_pupils_say_vote_to_keep_Zayn_in_the_X_Factor|title=Classmates seek support for East Bowling One Direction star Zayn Malik|work={{tsl|en|Telegraph & Argus||Bradford Telegraph & Argus}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Newsquest||Newsquest}} Media Group|date=2010-11-26|accessdate=2010-11-26|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626140636/http://www.thetelegraphandargus.co.uk/news/8689788.Tong_School_pupils_say_vote_to_keep_Zayn_in_the_X_Factor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>因为自己是混血的原因，馬利克并不适应在两个学校的生活。馬利克称自己从十二岁开始就对自己的外貌感到骄傲。<ref name="Dare to Dream">{{cite book|title=Dare to Dream: Life as One Direction|author=One Direction members|year=2011|publisher=[[哈珀柯林斯|HarperCollins]]|isbn=978-0-00-744439-7}} {{page needed|date=April 2013}}</ref> 

== 职业生平 ==
===2010年 - 2015年：{{引书号转换|X音素}}与1世代===
{{Main|1世代}}
[[File:Zayn_Malik,_2012.jpg|200px]]
2010年，马利克以个人身份参加了英國電視節目《[[X音素|X音素]]》的海選，但在比賽中遭到了淘汰。對於海選的失敗，马利克說道：“這是我在摸索經驗。”<ref name=MalikVEVO>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V1_nZZHOXd4&feature=plcp&context=C4af010eVDvjVQa1PpcFMGKY4ENQtZv7dQojv9xu6k-Lf8pueFhpk%3D|title=Zayn Interview (VEVO LIFT): Brought to you by McDonald's|publisher=YouTube|date=2012-03-30|accessdate=2012-04-27|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003085509/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V1_nZZHOXd4&feature=plcp&context=C4af010eVDvjVQa1PpcFMGKY4ENQtZv7dQojv9xu6k-Lf8pueFhpk%3D|dead-url=no}}</ref>評審之一，[[西蒙·高維爾|西蒙·高維爾]]不想埋沒他的才華，於是決定讓他和其他四名参賽者[[奈爾·霍蘭|奈爾·霍蘭]]、[[連恩·佩恩|連恩·佩恩]]、[[哈利·斯泰爾|哈利·斯泰爾]]和[[路易·湯姆林森|路易·湯姆林森]]組成團體[[1世代|1世代]]繼續比賽。在晉級《X音素》第七季決賽名單之後，馬利克和其他四人與西蒙·高維爾旗下的唱片公司[[賽科音樂|賽科]]簽約。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lee |first=Cara |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/tv/x_factor/3277896/Simon-Cowell-snaps-up-Cher-Rebecca-and-One-Direction.html |title=Simon Cowell snaps up Cher, Rebecca and One Direction | The Sun |Showbiz|TV|X Factor |publisher=The Sun |date=2010-12-15 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121200319/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/tv/x_factor/3277896/Simon-Cowell-snaps-up-Cher-Rebecca-and-One-Direction.html |archivedate=2011-11-21 }}</ref>在之后的比賽中，他們最終獲得了第三名的成績。隨後，他們在北美的音樂合約則簽給了[[索尼音樂娛樂|哥倫比亞唱片]]。<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a352201/one-direction-sign-us-record-deal-with-adele-label-columbia.html |title=One Direction sign US record deal with Adele label Columbia - Music News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2011-11-22 |accessdate=2012-01-14 |archive-date=2012-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125082425/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a352201/one-direction-sign-us-record-deal-with-adele-label-columbia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

马利克在1世代中以团体的名义发行了4张录音室专辑。2015年3月25日，馬利克因承受不住壓力與創作理念不同為由宣佈退出1世代。<ref name="smh.com.au">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/one-direction-singer-zayn-malik-quits-boyband-chooses-to-be-a-normal-22yearold-20150326-1m7thh.html|title=One Direction singer Zayn Malik quits boyband, chooses to be a 'normal 22-year-old'|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2015-08-19|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126132916/https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/one-direction-singer-zayn-malik-quits-boyband-chooses-to-be-a-normal-22yearold-20150326-1m7thh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/25/entertainment/feat-zayn-malik-leaving-one-direction/index.html|title=Zayn Malik leaving One Direction|author=Leopold, Todd|work=CNN|date=2015-03-26|access-date=2017-10-29|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923134651/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/25/entertainment/feat-zayn-malik-leaving-one-direction/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a638263/zayn-malik-on-one-direction-exit-ive-never-felt-more-in-control.html#~p8o92aIzTo7Rdu|title= Zayn Malik on One Direction exit: 'I've never felt more in control'|last1= Davies|first1= Megan|date= 2015-03-27|publisher= [[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|access-date= 2015-03-30|archive-date= 2015-09-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924162603/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a638263/zayn-malik-on-one-direction-exit-ive-never-felt-more-in-control.html#~p8o92aIzTo7Rdu|dead-url= no}}</ref>

===2015年 - 2016年：《心解密》===
2015年7月29日，马利克宣布与[[RCA唱片|RCA唱片]]签约。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Strecker|first1=Erin|title=Zayn Malik Signs With RCA, Tweets Excitement|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6648505/zayn-malik-signs-rca|accessdate=2015-07-29|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|agency=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-07-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6aSU2QMs5?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6648505/zayn-malik-signs-rca|archivedate=2015-08-01|location=United States|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2016年1月，馬利克透露了個人首張專輯的名字為《{{Link-en|心解密|Mind of Mine}}》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/28/zayn-malik-mind-of-mine | title=Zayn Malik reveals debut album title, plus more highlights from his Beats 1 interview with Zane Lowe | work=Entertainment Weekly | date=2016-01-28 | accessdate=2016-01-28 | archive-date=2021-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125101414/https://ew.com/article/2016/01/28/zayn-malik-mind-of-mine/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。專輯的首張單曲《[[枕邊情話|枕邊情話]]》于2016年1月29日和其音樂錄影帶共同發行<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6859197/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-video-released | title=Zayn Malik's Sexy 'Pillowtalk' Video is Here: Watch | work=Billboard | date=2016-01-29 | accessdate=2016-01-29 | author=Billboard Staff | archive-date=2019-01-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104080946/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6859197/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-video-released | dead-url=no }}</ref>，歌曲空降[[英國單曲榜|英國單曲榜]]<ref name="UK">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/49002/zayn/|title=Zayn > UK Charts|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]]|work=Officialcharts.com/|access-date=2016-05-23|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501175500/https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/49002/zayn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與美國[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]冠軍<ref name="uspillowtalk">{{cite web | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6867374/zayn-pillowtalk-debuts-no-1-hot-100 | title=Zayn's 'Pillowtalk' Debuts at No. 1 on Hot 100 | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=Billboard | date=2016-02-08 | accessdate=2016-02-08 | author=Trust, Gary | archive-date=2016-02-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208225756/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6867374/zayn-pillowtalk-debuts-no-1-hot-100 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年3月25日，專輯《心解密》正式發佈。<ref name="release">{{cite web | url=http://www.rcarecords.com/news/zayn-releases-pillowtalk | title=ZAYN Releases "PILLOWTALK" | publisher=RCA | date=2016-01-29 | accessdate=2016-01-30 | archive-date=2021-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128153148/https://www.rcarecords.com/news/zayn-releases-pillowtalk/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>《心解密》在美国[[告示牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌二百强专辑榜]]空降第1，首周获得了157,000份销售单元，其中纯专辑销量约有112,000份。<ref name="Billboard Mind of Mine">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7318826/zayn-malik-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200-albums-chart-with-mind-of-mine-pillowtalk|title=Zayn Debuts at No. 1 on Billboard 200 Albums Chart With 'Mind of Mine'|publisher=''[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]''|date=2016-04-04|accessdate=2016-04-04|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001115215/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7318826/zayn-malik-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200-albums-chart-with-mind-of-mine-pillowtalk|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《心解密》发行后，马利克称自己想攻读自己出道前一直想攻读的英文或文学的[[学位|学位]]，并在此期间创作他的第2张录音室专辑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2797002/zayn-complex-interview/|title=ZAYN PREVIEWS NEW SONG ‘MIND OF MINE’ AND TEASES HIS ‘VERY SEXUAL ALBUM’|website=[[音樂電視網|MTV]]|date=2016-03-21|access-date=2016-07-30|archive-date=2018-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919224323/http://www.mtv.com/news/2797002/zayn-complex-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年7月，馬利克與英國製作團隊Snakehips合作了單曲《{{lang|en|Cruel}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7438952/zayn-malik-snakehips-cruel?|title=Zayn Collaborates With Snakehips on Moody Single 'Cruel'|publisher=|access-date=2017-02-25|archive-date=2018-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919224502/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7438952/zayn-malik-snakehips-cruel|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月8日，馬利克與[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒·斯威夫特]]為電影《[[格雷的五十道陰影：束縛_(電影)|格雷的五十道陰影：束縛]]》演唱的原聲帶歌曲《[[無愛不活|無愛不活]]》發行。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brandie|first1=Lars|title=Taylor Swift and Zayn Malik Join Forces on 'Fifty Shades' Song 'I Don't Wanna Live Forever': Listen|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7616811/taylor-swift-zayn-malik-fifty-shades-i-dont-wanna-live-forever|accessdate=2016-12-10|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2016-12-08|location=United States|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525125521/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7616811/taylor-swift-zayn-malik-fifty-shades-i-dont-wanna-live-forever|dead-url=no}}</ref>

